#: app/index.html:44
msgid "Find My Device"
msgstr "Canfod Fy Nyfais"

#: app/index.html:45
msgid "Locate a lost phone, lock it or even erase it remotely."
msgstr "Canfod ffôn coll, ei gloi neu hyd yn oed ei ddileu o bell."

#: app/index.html:48
msgid "Sign in"
msgstr "Mewngofnodi"

#: app/index.html:49
msgid "Create a Firefox Account"
msgstr "Creu Cyfrif Firefox"

#: app/index.html:51
msgid ""
"If you’ve lost your Firefox OS smartphone, Find My Device can help you find "
"it. You can see it on a map, make it play a sound and have it display a "
"message. You can also lock it for safety or delete your personal info "
"completely."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych wedi colli eich ffôn Firefox OS, gan Canfod Fy Nyfais eich helpu i "
"ddod o hyd iddo. Mae modd i chi ei weld ar fap, gwneud iddo ganu tôn a "
"dangos neges. Gallwch hefyd ei gloi er diogelwch neu ddileu eich gwybodaeth "
"bersonol yn llwyr."

#: app/index.html:52
msgid ""
"To get started, make sure you have a Firefox Account and Find My Device "
"enabled on your phone."
msgstr ""
"I gychwyn arni, gwnewch yn siŵr fod gennych gyfrif Firefox a Canfod Fy "
"Nyfais wedi ei alluogi ar eich ffôn."

#: app/index.html:59
msgid "Track"
msgstr "Tracio"

#: app/index.html:60
msgid ""
"As long as your phone remains on and connected to the Internet, you can see "
"its location on the map."
msgstr ""
"Cyhyd a bod eich ffôn ymlaen ac wedi ei gysylltu â'r rhyngwyd, gallwch weld "
"ei leoliad ar y map."

#: app/index.html:63
msgid "Ring"
msgstr "Canu"

#: app/index.html:64
msgid ""
"If you see that it’s nearby on the map, you can make the phone ring, even if"
" the ringer is set to silent."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych yn gallu gweld o'r map ei fod gerllaw galwch wneud i'r ffôn ganu, "
"hyd yn oed os yw wedi ei osod i fod yn dawel."

#: app/index.html:67
msgid "Lock"
msgstr "Cloi"

#: app/index.html:68
msgid ""
"To protect your personal info, you can lock your screen and have it display "
"a message to help someone return it to you."
msgstr ""
"I ddiogelu eich gwybodaeth bersonol, gallwch gloi'r sgrin a dangos neges i "
"helpu rhywun ei ddychwelyd i chi."

#: app/index.html:71
msgid "Erase"
msgstr "Dileu"

#: app/index.html:72
msgid ""
"If you’re unable to find your phone, you can permanently erase it, but "
"please note that this can not be undone."
msgstr ""
"Os nad ydych yn gallu dod o hyd i'ch ffôn, gallwch ei ddileu'n barhaol ond "
"cofiwch had oes modd dadwneud hyn."

